commit.message:
Fix whitespace in pattern.

From-SVN: r7456

@@ -3939,13 +3939,13 @@

-  mr %0,%1
-  ld%U1%X1 %0,%1
-  sd%U0%X0 %1,%0
-  #
-  fmr %0,%1

 ;; Next come the multi-word integer load and store and the load and store
